  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Libwnck</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Libwnck</application> package contains a Window Navigator
      Construction Kit.
    </para>

    &lfs71_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informations sur le paquet</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>Téléchargement (HTTP)&nbsp;: <ulink url="&libwnck2-download-http;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Téléchargement (FTP)&nbsp;: <ulink url="&libwnck2-download-ftp;"/></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Somme de contrôle MD5 du téléchargement&nbsp;: &libwnck2-md5sum;</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Taille du téléchargement&nbsp;: &libwnck2-size;</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Estimation de l'espace disque requis&nbsp;: &libwnck2-buildsize;</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Estimation du temps de construction&nbsp;: &libwnck2-time;</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Libwnck Dependencies</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Requises</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="gtk2"/> et
      <xref linkend="intltool"/>.
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Facultatives</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="gobject-introspection"/>,
      <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/> et
      <xref linkend="startup-notification"/>.
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Notes utilisateur&nbsp;:
    <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/libwnck2"/></para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Libwnck</title>

    <para>
      Installez <application>Libwnck</application> en lançant les commandes
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static --program-suffix=-1 &amp;&amp;
make GETTEXT_PACKAGE=libwnck-1</userinput></screen>

    <para>Ce paquet n'est pas fourni avec une suite de tests.</para>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make GETTEXT_PACKAGE=libwnck-1 install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explications des commandes</title>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      href="../../xincludes/static-libraries.xml"/>

    <para>
      <option>--program-suffix=-1</option>: This option adds -1 to the end of
      the names of the installed programs to avoid overwriting the programs
      installed by <xref linkend="libwnck"/>.
    </para>

    <para>
      <parameter>GETTEXT_PACKAGE=libwnck-1</parameter>: This parameter adds -1
      to the end of the names of the gettext files installed by the package
      to avoid overwriting the files installed by <xref linkend="libwnck"/>.
    </para>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
    href="../../xincludes/gtk-doc-rebuild.xml"/>
  </sect2>

